stinctive sporting identity and humanist message\\\".\", \"from\": 799, \"to\": 962, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 799, \"end\": 804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ancient_Egypt\", \"score\": 0.7672556129928226, \"rank\": 0.3030213667403142, \"text\": \"Egypt\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ancient_Egypt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ancient_Egypt\"}, {\"begin\": 807, \"end\": 825, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anglican_Communion\", \"score\": 0.9991357331146882, \"rank\": 0.0008650144887467196, \"text\": \"Anglican Communion\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anglican_Communion\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anglican_Communion\"}, {\"begin\": 894, \"end\": 897, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9999999999820375, \"rank\": 1.7494648279241024e-11, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ceremony's artistic director, Thomas Jolly, distanced himself from any parallels with\\\"The Last Supper\\\"after the ceremony, saying it was aboutcelebrating diversityand paying homage to the feast andFrench gastronomy.\", \"from\": 964, \"to\": 1182, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 998, \"end\": 1004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\", \"score\": 0.9996259099672117, \"rank\": 0.0003711004061134179, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said he drew inspiration from the \\\"Festin des Dieux\\\" or Banquet of the Gods by Dutch painter Jan Harmensz van Bijlert.\", \"from\": 1184, \"to\": 1305, \"entities\": [{\"begin\